spec.help: Whether all filters in this group must return `true` (`And`), or one or more must return `true` (`Or`; not yet supported by Google Search Console API).
spec.name: groupType
spec.label: Group Type

expect.help: The grouping dimension values are combined to create a unique key for each result row. If no dimensions are specified, all values will be combined into a single row.
expect.name: dimensions
expect.label: Dimensions

expect.help:
Filters results to the selected type.
 - `Web`: Filter results to the combined ("All") tab in Google Search. Does not include Discover or Google News results.
 - `Image`: Search results from the "Image" tab in Google Search.
 - `Video`: Video search results.
 - `News`: Search results from the "News" tab in Google Search.
 - `Google News`: Results from `news.google.com` and the Google News app on Android and iOS. Doesn't include results from the "News" tab in Google Search.
expect.name: type
expect.label: Type

expect.help:
How data is aggregated. If aggregated `By Property`, all data for the same property is aggregated; if aggregated `By Page`, all data is aggregated by canonical URI. If you filter or group by page, choose `Auto`; otherwise you can aggregate either `By Property` or `By Page`, depending on how you want your data calculated.
**Note:** if you group or filter by page, you cannot aggregate by property.
expect.name: aggregationType
expect.label: Aggregation Type

expect.help: If `All`, data will include fresh data. If `Final` or if this parameter is omitted, the returned data will include only finalized data.
expect.name: dataState
expect.label: Data State

expect.help: The maximum number of results to be worked with during one execution cycle.
expect.name: limit
expect.label: Limit

searchAnalytics.description: Searches traffic data for the specified URL.
